model.environment.objects.physicalObject

Class PhysicalObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.environment.map.MapComponent
      • model.environment.objects.physicalObject.PhysicalObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PolygonShape, SimulationObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Chair, Desk, QueueSeparator, Wall, XRaySystem

    public abstract class PhysicalObject
extends MapComponent
implements PolygonShape
    A physical obstacle is an object that cannot be accessed by HumanAgents. It is represented by a list of corner points, of which the first one is the top left corner of the obstacle.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
